data.description: China Spring ISD! 3 bedroom 2 bath on 1.1+/- Acre lot! There is a 2 car attached garage and then a detached carport tall enough for RV or big enough for several cars. It has an attached storage room on the left side and a workshop on the backside. Behind the workshop is a great gardening shed. This home has a great layout with open living, kitchen, dining. The living room features a built-in wood stove. There is vinyl plank flooring throughout the home! There is also a large covered patio.
